`jde-parse-get-top-of-class' for more information.

NO-MOVE-POINT if non-nil just the position is returned, otherwise the point is
moved also."
  (if (= (point) (jde-parse-get-top-of-class class-regexp no-move-point))
      (insert "\n"))
  (insert "\n")
  (backward-char 1))

