Setting this variable defines a template instantiation command
`jde-gen-equals-method', as a side-effect."
  :group 'jde-gen
  :type '(repeat string)
  :set '(lambda (sym val)
	  (defalias 'jde-gen-equals-method
	    (tempo-define-template
